## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="edfcc-268"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> dá suporte a conversões implícitas de classes a seguir:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="edfcc-268"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> supports implicit conversions from the following classes:</span></span>  
  
