 <span data-ttu-id="edfcc-354">O exemplo a seguir cria uma gramática de reconhecimento de fala frases como "Chamada James no trabalho" e "Anne de chamada no seu celular", onde a palavra "phone" é opcional.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="edfcc-354">The following example creates a speech recognition grammar for phrases such as "Call James at work" and "Call Anne on her cell phone", where the word "phone" is optional.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="edfcc-355"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> e <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> objetos são usados para construir a gramática.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="edfcc-355"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> objects are used to construct the grammar.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="edfcc-356">O exemplo destaca o uso do <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.Append%2A> método.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="edfcc-356">The example highlights the use of the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.Append%2A> method.</span></span>  
  
